## 11. Sistema de Pagamentos (Mercado Pago)

### Arquivo: [mercadopago.ts](file:///d:/Nova%20pasta/Agencia-Fashion/campanha-ia/src/lib/payments/mercadopago.ts)

### Fluxo de Assinatura

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Usuário
    participant F as Frontend (/plano)
    participant API as POST /api/checkout
    participant MP as Mercado Pago
    participant WH as POST /api/webhooks/mercadopago
    participant DB as Supabase

    U->>F: Seleciona plano
    F->>API: planId + storeId
    API->>MP: createSubscription() (PreApproval)
    MP-->>API: init_point URL
    API-->>F: Redirect URL
    F->>MP: Usuário preenche cartão
    MP->>WH: Webhook (payment.approved)
    WH->>DB: updateStorePlan() + store_usage reset
    WH-->>MP: 200 OK
```

### Fluxo de Créditos Avulsos

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Usuário
    participant F as Frontend (/plano)
    participant API as POST /api/credits
    participant MP as Mercado Pago
    participant WH as Webhook
    participant DB as Supabase

    U->>F: Seleciona pacote de créditos
    F->>API: packageId + storeId
    API->>MP: Preference (pagamento único)
    MP-->>API: init_point URL
    API-->>F: Redirect URL
    F->>MP: Pagamento
    MP->>WH: Webhook (payment.approved)
    WH->>DB: addCreditsToStore()
    WH-->>MP: 200 OK
```

### Funções de Pagamento

| Função | Descrição |
|---|---|
| `createSubscription()` | Cria assinatura recorrente via PreApproval API |
| `cancelSubscription()` | Cancela assinatura ativa |
| `getSubscriptionStatus()` | Consulta status da assinatura |
| `createCheckoutPreference()` | Cria pagamento único via Preference API |
| `getPaymentStatus()` | Consulta status de pagamento |

